N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5303.4 - Photograph

State Regulations

Each applicant, licensee or registrant who is a natural
person shall submit with his or her application a color photograph in the
format required by the application. Such photograph is required to have been
taken within six months of the date the application is submitted to the
commission. Notes
